OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FArchbishop of Canterbury Sarah
OL,7,FMullally's presence in Rome is giving
OL,8,Fsome female Catholics hope, as ITV
OL,9,FNews' Julie Etchingham reports
OL,11,FIn the hallowed chambers of the
OL,12,FApostolic Palace at the Vatican, there
OL,13,Fwas a moment of church history today.
OL,15,FFor sixty years, there have been
OL,16,Fmeetings between Popes and Archbishops
OL,17,Fof Canterbury, with ever warmer
OL,18,Frelations between the Roman Catholic
OL,19,Fand Anglican Church - split in such
OL,20,Fbloody fashion by the Reformation
OL,21,Fnearly 500 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
