PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FBut never has that visiting Archbishop
OL,7,Fbeen a woman.
OL,9,FJust a month since Dame Sarah Mullally
OL,10,Fmade history as she was installed as
OL,11,Fthe leader of nearly 100 million
OL,12,FAnglicans around the world, she made
OL,13,Fit again today, by being received and
OL,14,Fwelcomed warmly by Pope Leo.
OL,16,FIt's significant, of course, because
OL,17,Fthe Roman Catholic Church does not
OL,18,Fpermit women to be ordained as priests
OL,19,F- let alone as bishops or archbishops,
OL,20,Fand there is no sign of that changing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FSo the very sight and fact of
OL,7,FArchbishop Mullally being welcomed at
OL,8,Fthe heart of the Roman Catholic Church
OL,9,Fis extraordinary and will reverberate
OL,10,Faround the global churches.
OL,12,FIt was a fascinating encounter.
OL,13,FNeither leader is a natural extrovert
OL,14,F- there was no effusive greeting
OL,15,Fbefore them - but there was warm
OL,16,Frespect between the pair, who have
OL,17,Falready called one another brother and
OL,18,Fsister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FPerhaps both would have been conscious
OL,7,Fthat the image would be controversial
OL,8,Ffor parts of their congregations.
OL,10,FCertainly in some parts of the global
OL,11,Fsouth of worldwide Anglican Communion
OL,12,Fwho reject a woman being made
OL,13,Farchbishop to lead them.
OL,15,FDame Sarah Mullally - who has recently
OL,16,Fsupported Pope Leo in his speaking out
OL,17,Fagainst Trump's war in Iran - paid
OL,18,Ftribute to Leo's efforts to speak of
OL,19,Fhope in world of injustice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FIn return, though openly acknowledging
OL,7,Fwhat he admitted were 'intractable
OL,8,Fdifferences' between the two Churches,
OL,9,FPope Leo said it would be a 'scandal'
OL,10,Fif they didn't work to resolve them
OL,11,Fand to join forces in advancing a
OL,12,Fmessage of peace.
OL,14,FIn another eye-popping sight, the two
OL,15,Fthen sang and prayed together in a
OL,16,Fchapel in the heart of the Vatican.
OL,17,FSuch an event would have been
OL,18,Funthinkable even a few years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FIt is an inescapable fact, however,
OL,7,Fdespite the clear respect between the
OL,8,Ftwo, Archbishop Mullally embodies one
OL,9,Fof the deepest differences between the
OL,10,Fchurches.
OL,12,FJust yesterday in Rome, Pope Leo
OL,13,Fordained ten candidates to the all-
OL,14,Fmale priesthood.
OL,16,FFor some senior Roman Catholic women
OL,17,Fhere in Rome, Archbishop Mullally's
OL,18,Fvisit presents a moment of personal
OL,19,Fhope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FI met Sister Roxanne Schares, an
OL,7,FAmerican religious sister and
OL,8,FExecutive Secretary of the
OL,9,FInternational Union of Superiors
OL,10,FGeneral.
OL,12,FShe's due to meet Archbishop Mullally
OL,13,Fon Tuesday in what will be a personal
OL,14,Fmoment of hope.
OL,16,F"As a child, I probably longed to be
OL,17,Fordained myself, but as I have lived
OL,18,Fmy religious life, I find I don't need
OL,19,Fordination to be engaged fully in
OL,20,Fministry," she told me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,F"There are many women in the Catholic
OL,7,FChurch longing for the possibility of
OL,8,Fordination to be priest or deacons -
OL,9,Fthere are other women who are at a
OL,10,Fdifferent place because of their
OL,11,Fcontext, their culture, the realities
OL,12,Fthey deal with. So I think there's a
OL,13,Fwhole range of where women are in
OL,14,Fthis", Sister Roxanne Schares added.
OL,16,FArchbishop Mullally's visit is not the
OL,17,Fonly outward sign of a deepening
OL,18,Ffriendship between the once bitterly
OL,19,Fdivided churches.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FIt follows hot on the heels of the
OL,7,FKing's visit last October, where as
OL,8,FVatican expert here in Rome Nicole
OL,9,FWinfield told me, not just church but
OL,10,Fglobal history was made.
OL,12,F"That was a historic moment. That was
OL,13,Fthe first time since the Reformation
OL,14,Fthat we had seen the two titular heads
OL,15,Fof the churches praying together," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FWinfield added that Archbishop
OL,19,FMullally's visit is a follow-up for
OL,20,Fthat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,F"For the Vatican, I think this is just
OL,7,Fanother step in this ongoing dialogue,
OL,8,Fand a chance to show a willingness to
OL,9,Fcontinue it", she explained.
OL,11,FAt the end of the groundbreaking
OL,12,Fencounter between this former chief
OL,13,Fnurse and the pontiff, there was an
OL,14,Fexchange of gifts, including a pot of
OL,15,Fhoney from Lambeth Palace.
OL,17,FThere was also assurance of a warm
OL,18,Fwelcome if he ever comes to Britain -
OL,19,Fthough it's not clear if that's on the
OL,20,Fagenda yet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777392671
OL,3,CA moment of church history as Dame
OL,4,CSarah Mullally meets the Pope
OL,6,FIt's notable, of course, that
OL,7,FArchbishop Mullally's meeting with one
OL,8,Fof the world's two most famous
OL,9,FAmericans comes at the same time as
OL,10,Fthe King's visit to the other.
OL,12,FWhere one US-UK special relationship
OL,13,Fmay be showing the strain, there is
OL,14,Fanother which began today here in Rome
OL,15,Fwhich these two leaders hope will bear
OL,16,Ffruit.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
